{"tid":2075954,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「反送中」藏書親建制　撐抗爭書 0 入選　公共圖書館否認偏頗","createTime":"2020-06-23T07:27:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-23T08:53:06.000Z","uid":34722,"like":14,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"ae0104905db6c1b1053af152625e6a4d7585aec9","tid":2075954,"uid":34722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T07:27:03.000Z","msg":"轉載立場新聞:<br />\n由「反送中」引發的社會抗爭至今一年，建制與非建制陣營均推出多本相關著作。香港公共圖書館購入部分書籍，但根據本網分析，選書傾向建制，支持抗爭陣營著作無一獲藏。有學者形容藏書情況「呈現官方姿態意味」。圖書館則指，館方「不會利用館藏宣揚任何特定信念或觀點」，並強調館藏需要符合香港法律，「不能有鼓勵讀者犯法的內容和建議」。<br />\n<br />\n《立場新聞》向獨立書店查詢，並到三聯書店視察，整合網上資料，發現過去一年（2019 年 6 月至 2020 年 5 月）與「反送中」相關已出版的書籍共有最少 27 本，主要可分成建制陣營出版、聲援抗爭陣營、中立／無明顯政治傾向、宗教出版及文學著作五大類。香港公共圖書館確認已入購其中9本，包括建制陣營的《哭泣的城市：香港修例風波實錄》、《一場集體催眠》、《國際視野中的香港修例風波》、《香港「修例風波」真相》、《香港 2020：治亂交替與危中之機》、《思考香港一國兩制的未來》，而聲援抗爭陣營的著作則無一獲藏。每項書目平均購置約數十本。<br />\n<br />\n全文:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/culture/%E5%8F%8D%E9%80%81%E4%B8%AD-%E8%97%8F%E6%9B%B8%E8%A6%AA%E5%BB%BA%E5%88%B6-%E6%92%90%E6%8A%97%E7%88%AD%E6%9B%B8-0-%E5%85%A5%E9%81%B8-%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E5%9C%96%E6%9B%B8%E9%A4%A8%E5%90%A6%E8%AA%8D%E5%81%8F%E9%A0%97/?fbclid=IwAR3uckPOv8qb_Eqpwsq1Xug7er4PWT0CkaG_DWNmBlqwlXzNQiXjfY4ZuSI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fculture%2F%25E5%258F%258D%25E9%2580%2581%25E4%25B8%25AD-%25E8%2597%258F%25E6%259B%25B8%25E8%25A6%25AA%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E5%2588%25B6-%25E6%2592%2590%25E6%258A%2597%25E7%2588%25AD%25E6%259B%25B8-0-%25E5%2585%25A5%25E9%2581%25B8-%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%2585%25B1%25E5%259C%2596%25E6%259B%25B8%25E9%25A4%25A8%25E5%2590%25A6%25E8%25AA%258D%25E5%2581%258F%25E9%25A0%2597%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3uckPOv8qb_Eqpwsq1Xug7er4PWT0CkaG_DWNmBlqwlXzNQiXjfY4ZuSI&d=%2FOWxXeQsMLcQIgbDBmmt7le0bVP%2BLlUkdLfYKyPPBhg%3D&h=cd8e8e85\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fculture%2F%25E5%258F%258D%25E9%2580%2581%25E4%25B8%25AD-%25E8%2597%258F%25E6%259B%25B8%25E8%25A6%25AA%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E5%2588%25B6-%25E6%2592%2590%25E6%258A%2597%25E7%2588%25AD%25E6%259B%25B8-0-%25E5%2585%25A5%25E9%2581%25B8-%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%2585%25B1%25E5%259C%2596%25E6%259B%25B8%25E9%25A4%25A8%25E5%2590%25A6%25E8%25AA%258D%25E5%2581%258F%25E9%25A0%2597%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3uckPOv8qb_Eqpwsq1Xug7er4PWT0CkaG_DWNmBlqwlXzNQiXjfY4ZuSI&h=7d041572\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/culture/%E5%8F%8D%E9%80%81%E4%B8%AD-%E8%97%8F%E6%9B%B8%E8%A6%AA%E5%BB%BA%E5%88%B6-%E6%92%90%E6%8A%97%E7%88%AD%E6%9B%B8-0-%E5%85%A5%E9%81%B8-%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E5%9C%96%E6%9B%B8%E9%A4%A8%E5%90%A6%E8%AA%8D%E5%81%8F%E9%A0%97/?fbclid=IwAR3uckPOv8qb_Eqpwsq1Xug7er4PWT0CkaG_DWNmBlqwlXzNQiXjfY4ZuSI</a><br />\n<br />\n連陳雲本城邦論圖書館都有，但《自由六月》依本咁溫和都無份入選。仲有大公報出個本文集有; 李怡果本就無，紫荊雜誌社出既就有，端傳媒出既圖集就無; 王振民、劉兆佳出既就有，其他學者既就無; 而叫做「中立」D 果本係周顯寫既......"},{"pid":"ad669babf7a0be7213009c8a67686e6274aee974","tid":2075954,"uid":71676,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T07:32:01.000Z","msg":"篡改歷史+洗腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f904c855f79abb1c83ee37ff880332959aef303b","tid":2075954,"uid":199893,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T07:32:59.000Z","msg":"冇錯 所以唔會有政治中立"},{"pid":"267dac5592bff99dd23a64800c551a1921112eec","tid":2075954,"uid":199893,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T07:33:26.000Z","msg":"任何可以成為打壓嘅工具 都必然會成為打壓嘅工具"},{"pid":"abe08573bcc556880b5e5be338299324f3657698","tid":2075954,"uid":244818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T07:33:29.000Z","msg":"借個位 會員標籤功能 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1880412\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1880412</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64a18a15a2a376e87c7aa64be937daf007c49231","tid":2075954,"uid":49018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T07:33:43.000Z","msg":"［行動Post］7月11-12日全香港要人<br />\n<a href=\"http